column4: Three lanes outbound and one lane inbound from 6:30 p.m. to 8:30 p.m. for post-game traffic.
No left turn from outbound Nicholasville to Alumni.
Alumni Dr is ONE WAY from the stadium to Nicholasville Rd.

column3: Tates Creek Rd at Alumni Dr:
column4: Outbound Tates Creek traffic coming from Cooper Dr MUST turn left to Alumni.

column3: Tates Creek Rd at Alumni Dr:
column4: Inbound Tates Creek left turn to Alumni is CLOSED.

column3: Tates Creek Rd at Alumni Dr:
column4: All traffic from the stadium must turn right to Tates Creek Rd.
Cooper Dr is ONE WAY from the stadium to Tates Creek.
Waller Ave is ONE WAY from Nicholasville Rd to Harrodsburg Rd.
